Junius Daniel

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Junius Daniel





Born
(1828-06-27)June 27, 1828
Halifax, North Carolina


Died
May 13, 1864(1864-05-13) (aged 35)
Spotsylvania County, Virginia


Allegiance
