Insider Activity


Individual




Daniel M. Junius



Mr. Daniel M. Junius is Independent Director at IDEXX Laboratories, Inc., Chief Financial Officer at Deluxepinpoint Co. and Treasurer & Director at Biotechnology Industry Organization. He is on the Board of Directors at GlycoMimetics, Inc., IDEXX Laboratories, Inc., ImmunoGen, Inc. and Biotechnology Industry Organization. Mr. Junius was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by New England Business Service, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Nashua Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Boston College and a graduate degree from Kellogg School of Management.



