                                                    BRIEF-Idexx Laboratories elects Stuart Essig to the board
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    4:27 PM ET 07/17/2017
                                                


Idexx Laboratories Inc (IDXX). * Idexx Laboratories (IDXX) elects Stuart M. Essig to board of directors. * Idexx Laboratories Inc (IDXX) - In connection with Dr. Essig's election, board also increased its size from 8 to 9 members, effective July 12, 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories Elects Stuart M. Essig to Board of Directors
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:15 PM ET 07/17/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, July 17, 2017  IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX), a global leader in veterinary diagnostics, veterinary practice software and water microbiology testing, today announced the unanimous election of Stuart M. Essig as a member of the Company's Board of Directors, effective July 12, 2017.

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories to Release 2017 Second Quarter Financial Results
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    1:08 PM ET 07/10/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, July 10, 2017 IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX) has scheduled the release of its 2017 second quarter financial results for Tuesday, August 1, at approximately 7:00 a.m. ET. The Company will conduct an analyst conference call beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET on that day.

















                                                    Healthcare Stocks on Investors' Radar -- PAREXEL, IDEXX Labs, ICON PLC, and PRA Health Sciences
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    6:50 AM ET 06/09/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, June 9, 2017 On Thursday, June 08, 2017, US markets saw a mixed session as 4 sectors closed in green, 3 sectors finished in red, and 2 sectors ended flat for the day. http://dailystocktracker.com/register/ PAREXEL . Waltham, Massachusetts headquartered PAREXEL International Corp.'s (PRXL) stock finished Thursday's session 1.23% higher at $82.61 with a total trading volume of 508,349 shares.

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories to Present at William Blair Growth Stock Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    3:00 PM ET 06/01/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, June 1, 2017  IDEXX Laboratories (IDXX), Inc., a global leader in veterinary diagnostics, veterinary practice software and water microbiology testing, announced today that it will participate in the William Blair 37th Annual Growth Stock Conference.

















                                                    BRIEF-Idexx Labs director End sells 5,000 shares of co's common stock on May 22
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    8:30 AM ET 05/23/2017
                                                


Idexx Laboratories Inc (IDXX). * Idexx Laboratories (IDXX) director William End reports sale of 5,000 shares of co's common stock on May 22 at average price of $162.55 per share - SEC filing Source text: http://bit.ly/2qSclJO Further company coverage:

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories to Present at Stifel 2017 Dental and Veterinary Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    3:00 PM ET 05/17/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, May 17, 2017 IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX), a global leader in veterinary diagnostics, veterinary practice software and water microbiology testing, announced today that it will participate in the Stifel Dental and Veterinary Conference.

















                                                    The 10 best, 10 worst U.S. stocks of 2017
                                                


                                                    MarketWatch – 
                                                    7:26 AM ET 05/07/2017
                                                


The S&P 500 Index is up 7%, helped by tech, consumer and health-care companies. The big milestone on everybody's mind over the past week has been President Trump's first 100 days in office. But with one-third of 2017 in the books, we thought it might be useful to see which stocks have had the best and worst performance so far this year.

















                                                    BRIEF-Idexx Laboratories reports increase in share repurchase program
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    7:21 AM ET 05/03/2017
                                                


Idexx Laboratories Inc (IDXX): * To repurchase up to an additional 3.0 million shares of its common stock under its ongoing share repurchase program. * Idexx Laboratories (IDXX) announces increase in share repurchase program Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories Announces Increase in Share Repurchase Program
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    7:00 AM ET 05/03/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, May 3, 2017  IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX), a global leader in veterinary diagnostics, veterinary practice software and water microbiology testing, today announced that the repurchase by the Company of up to an additional 3.0 million shares of its common stock under its ongoing share repurchase program has been authorized.

















                                                    BRIEF-Idexx Laboratories reports Q1 EPS $0.77
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    7:16 AM ET 04/28/2017
                                                


Idexx Laboratories Inc (IDXX). * Sees FY earnings per share of $2.95 to $3.11. * Idexx Laboratories (IDXX) announces first quarter results. * Q1 earnings per share $0.77. * Q1 revenue rose 11 percent to $462 million. * Says increases 2017 eps outlook range by $0.10 to $2.95 - $3.11. * Says raising its 2017 revenue outlook by $15 million to $1,925 million - $1,950 million.

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories Announces First Quarter Results
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    7:00 AM ET 04/28/2017
                                                


WESTBROOK, Maine, April 28, 2017 IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX), a global leader in veterinary diagnostics, veterinary practice software and water microbiology testing, reports revenues for the first quarter of 2017 of $462 million, an increase of 11% compared to the prior year period on both a reported and an organic basis.

















                                                    IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. to Join the NASDAQ-100 Index Beginning March 20, 2017
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    8:00 PM ET 03/10/2017
                                                


Nasdaq today announced that IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX), will become a component of the NASDAQ-100 Index®, the NASDAQ-100 Equal Weighted Index and the NASDAQ-100 Ex Technology Index prior to market open on Monday, March 20, 2017. IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (IDXX) is headquartered in Westbrook, Maine, and has a market capitalization of approximately $12.9 billion.












